name: React JS
author: Alexjander
details: React (also known as React. js or ReactJS) is a free and open-source front-end JavaScript library for building user interfaces based on UI components. It is maintained by Meta (formerly Facebook) and a community of individual developers and companies. React makes it painless to create interactive UIs.
